short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Records your youtube recommendations every week.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Have you ever watched someone open up their Youtube homepage and suddenly get a glimpse into their soul?

We change and evolve day by day, and slowly a machine that sits somewhere across the world absorbs our changes and reflects back the things we want to see and also ourselves.

This extension takes a snapshot of your Youtube recommendations every week and lets you jump through time to see what kind of person you were, or – if you believe that machine learning models are conscious – what kind of person your feed was.

All data is stored locally, nothing is collected or sent to the internet. The extension only kicks in when you are on "youtube.com" and no other paths or domains.
